reviewText: Bizarre and incoherent. If you like that sort of thing - go for it.
Wow, was this a highschool project?
I dare anyone to sit through this entire movie. If this is the first review you read, don't look at any others and go and watch this movie. I DARE YOU.....
bizarre, intermixed with a lot of WTF. too bad, because i expected it to be interesting, and perhaps it is, but I couldn't bring myself to watch more than 20 minutes.

Ken Russell said that thia was the best movies in many years. I tend to agree. Sure it's not for the typical gorehound and it shound not be so. It's surreal and artitistic. Abd this tasks it masters greatly.
